import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['year'])]
    data = data.sort_values(by='year')
    plt.plot(data['year'], data['net_generation'], color='blue')
    plt.axhline(y=data['net_generation'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', label='Mean')
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('Net Generation')
    plt.title('What is the trend of net generation over the years?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.groupby(['source', 'year']).sum().reset_index()
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    sources = data['source'].unique()
    colors = ['blue', 'orange', 'green', 'red', 'purple', 'brown', 'pink', 'gray', 'olive', 'cyan']
    bottom = None
    for i, source in enumerate(sources):
        source_data = data[data['source'] == source]
        ax.bar(source_data['year'], source_data['net_generation'], bottom=bottom, color=colors[i], label=source)
        if bottom is None:
            bottom = source_data['net_generation']
        else:
            bottom += source_data['net_generation']
    ax.set_xlabel('Year')
    ax.set_ylabel('Net Generation')
    ax.set_title('What is the distribution of net generation by source?')
    ax.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.groupby('source').mean()
    ax = data.plot(kind='bar', y='net_generation', legend=False)
    ax.axhline(y=data['net_generation'].mean(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Average')
    ax.set_xlabel('Source')
    ax.set_ylabel('Average Net Generation')
    ax.set_title('What is the average net generation by source?')
    ax.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y')
    data = data.pivot_table(index='year', columns='source', values='net_generation', aggfunc='sum')
    ax = sns.heatmap(data, cmap='YlGnBu', annot=True, fmt='.2f', linewidths=.5)
    ax.set_xlabel('Source')
    ax.set_ylabel('Year')
    ax.set_title('What is the total net generation by year and source?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```
